      <data key="d4">An episode can have a genre, describing the type or category of the content</data>
      <data key="d5">0dda79c5a216edd70f4e70acaf4cd810</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="GENRE" target="DURATION">
      <data key="d3">6.0</data>
      <data key="d4">A genre can have a duration, describing the length of the content in minutes</data>
